    "content": {
        "rendered": "<h2>Basic Setup</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Create a new Field Group</li>\n<li>Add an Email field</li>\n<li>Configure options:\n<ul>\n<li>Set placeholder text</li>\n<li>Add prepend/append text</li>\n<li>Configure validation</li>\n<li>Set default value</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Common Use Cases</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Contact Information\n<ul>\n<li>Contact forms</li>\n<li>User profiles</li>\n<li>Directory listings</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Notification Settings\n<ul>\n<li>Alert recipients</li>\n<li>Newsletter subscriptions</li>\n<li>System notifications</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Tips</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Use clear validation messages</li>\n<li>Consider multiple email support</li>\n<li>Add helpful placeholder text</li>\n<li>Validate email format</li>\n</ul>\n",
